                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Curacao</placeName>\n                <date>8 Sept 1859</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>Dear Sir!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Your esteemed lines of the<lb/>\n                <date>26 July</date> is duly received, where I noted with<lb/> much pleasure your\n                good health &amp;c<lb/> The object of this is to inform you that with<lb/> this date\n                I remit to <persName>Messrs Dovale &amp; Co</persName> Ninety<lb/> four dollars\n                80/00 to be forward to you for my a/c<lb/> which sum is of 5 <sic>setts</sic> books\n                I sold, as specify„<lb/>„ing here below, this time I had to make a discount<lb/> of\n                10 pct. I hope you will be satisfied; I think<lb/> to have soon another order for\n                some <sic>setts</sic>, I will<lb/> advice you to send 3 setts of Prayers books and 3\n                of Pen<lb/>tateuchs as it remains none in hand. I request<lb/> you to send me one\n                copy of <persName>Bendeman's</persName> “<persName>Jere<lb/>miah</persName> on the\n                ruins of <placeName><sic>Jerusalm</sic></placeName>” also one edi<lb/>„tion of\n                select sentences, their value shall be re<lb/>„mitted immediately. I send you\n                    <sic>inclose</sic> some<lb/> information regarding our <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                    >Medrash</hi> I hope<lb/> it will deserve a place in your periodical.<lb/>\n                <persName>Hoham Chaimaeiro<add>?</add></persName> send his good wishes to you<lb/>\n                without further for the present I am yours &amp;c</p>\n            <p>\n                <persName role=\"author\">B. de Casseres Jr</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">Note</hi>\n            </p>\n            <table cols=\"2\" rows=\"8\">\n                <row>\n                    <cell>2 setts Prayers books (<add>?</add>)</cell>\n                    <cell>$48</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>1 “<add>?</add>\n                        <add>?</add></cell>\n                    <cell>20</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>2 “Pentateuch</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\">24</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>$92</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>10 % Discount on them</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\"> 9.20</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>$82.80</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>4 subscribers of occid:</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\"> 12</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>$94.80</cell>\n                </row>\n            </table>\n            <p>Turn Over</p>\n            "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3tx35s46/canvas/p1"
                }
